org.apache.ignite.visor.commands.cache

VisorCacheClearCommand

Related Docs: object VisorCacheClearCommand | package cache

class VisorCacheClearCommand extends AnyRef

Overview

Visor 'clear' command implementation.

Help

+------------------------------------------------------------+
| cache -clear | Clears all entries from cache on all nodes. |
+------------------------------------------------------------+
Specification
cache -clear
cache -clear -c=<cache-name>
Arguments
<cache-name>
    Name of the cache.
    If not specified, default cache will be cleared.
Examples
cache -clear
    Clears interactively selected cache.
cache -clear -c=cache
    Clears cache with name 'cache'.
